{
  "texts": [
    "As part of search and selection process to identify the relevant academic literature, seven studies were included in the evaluation process.",
    "The flowchart of the search and selection process is illustrated in Figure 2.",
    "Although the search parameters were set to span a 15-year period from 2008 to September 2023, all publications included in the evaluation were published within the last 3 years.",
    "Two of the included articles had not yet undergone peer review at the time of data collection (Ducrée et al., 2022; Dehouche et al., 2023).",
    "Two of the included publications were published by the same first author (Ding et al., 2022; Ding et al., 2023), who was also a co-author of another included publication (Wang et al., 2022)."
  ]
}